001package react4j.dom.proptypes.html;
002
003import javax.annotation.Nonnull;
004import javax.annotation.Nullable;
005import jsinterop.annotations.JsOverlay;
006import jsinterop.annotations.JsPackage;
007import jsinterop.annotations.JsType;
008import org.intellij.lang.annotations.MagicConstant;

016/**
017 * Props for audio elements. Refer to http://www.w3schools.com/tags/tag_audio.asp
018 */
019@JsType( isNative = true, namespace = JsPackage.GLOBAL, name = "Object" )
020public class AudioProps
021  extends HtmlGlobalFields<AudioProps>
022{
023  @JsOverlay
024  @Nonnull
025  public final AudioProps autoPlay()
026  {
027    return autoPlay( true );
028  }
029
030  @JsOverlay
031  @Nonnull
032  public final AudioProps autoPlay( boolean b )
033  {
034    setAutoPlay( b );
035    return self();
036  }
037
038  @JsOverlay
039  @Nonnull
040  public final AudioProps controls()
041  {
042    return controls( true );
043  }
044
045  @JsOverlay
046  @Nonnull
047  public final AudioProps controls( boolean b )
048  {
049    setControls( b );
050    return self();
051  }
052
053  @JsOverlay
054  @Nonnull
055  public final AudioProps loop()
056  {
057    return loop( true );
058  }
059
060  @JsOverlay
061  @Nonnull
062  public final AudioProps loop( boolean b )
063  {
064    setLoop( b );
065    return self();
066  }
067
068  @JsOverlay
069  @Nonnull
070  public final AudioProps muted()
071  {
072    return muted( true );
073  }
074
075  @JsOverlay
076  @Nonnull
077  public final AudioProps muted( boolean b )
078  {
079    setMuted( b );
080    return self();
081  }
082
083  @JsOverlay
084  @Nonnull
085  public final AudioProps preLoad( @MagicConstant( valuesFromClass = AudioPreload.class ) final String value )
086  {
087    setPreload( value );
088    return self();
089  }
090
091  @JsOverlay
092  @Nonnull
093  public final AudioProps src( String s )
094  {
095    setSrc( s );
096    return self();
097  }
